title: Beach Burgerz
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Burger place across the street from the ocean. Has a veggie burgers section on menu with 3 vegan burgers and 1 vegetarian burger. Makes food to-order. Has vegan cheese, vegan mayo, vegan sriracha aoili, and sprouted bread for burger fixings. Order at the counter.
